objects.name: config
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE config (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, "key" VARCHAR UNIQUE, bell INTEGER DEFAULT (0), ban INTEGER DEFAULT (0), userid VARCHAR)

objects.name: contact
objects.ddl:
CREATE TABLE contact (
    id     INTEGER       NOT NULL,
    name   VARCHAR (64)  NOT NULL,
    icon   VARCHAR (255),
    userid VARCHAR (64)  NOT NULL,
    primary key (id ,userid) 
)

objects.name: contact_phone
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE contact_phone (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, country_no INTEGER, phone_no VARCHAR, type INTEGER, contact_no INTEGER NOT NULL, userid VARCHAR (64))

objects.name: db_version
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE db_version (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY, version INTEGER)

objects.name: history
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE history (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL DEFAULT (datetime('now', 'localtime')), state INT (64) DEFAULT (0), type INT (64) DEFAULT (0), content VARCHAR, tophone VARCHAR (64), fromphone VARCHAR (64), time integer (128), isread INTEGER (64), "index" UNIQUE, userid VARCHAR (64))

objects.name: photo
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE photo (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, small_url VARCHAR, big_url VARCHAR, width INTEGER, height INTEGER, isupload INTEGER, filename VARCHAR, filetype VARCHAR, userid VARCHAR (64))

objects.name: recent
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE recent (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, message_id INTEGER, userid VARCHAR, targetPhone VARCHAR UNIQUE, "index" INTEGER)

objects.name: wold_country
objects.ddl: CREATE TABLE wold_country (id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT, country_en VARCHAR (64) DEFAULT NULL, country_cn VARCHAR (64) DEFAULT NULL, country_code VARCHAR (16) DEFAULT NULL, continent VARCHAR (64) DEFAULT NULL, country_no VARCHAR (16) DEFAULT NULL, status INT (16) DEFAULT NULL)
